    "description": "We at Berger Silk Store Advisory Limited are looking for an experienced Department Manager based out of Nashik. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Berger Silk Store Advisory Limited:\nBerger Silk Store Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nashik, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Berger Silk Store Advisory Limited!",
